  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2007-06-28",
    "date": "2008-01-30T17:40:16Z",
    "text": "Greater Access to Education Act of 2007 - Amends Internal Revenue Code provisions relating to the Hope Scholarship tax credit to: (1) include room, board, fees, books, supplies, and equipment as expenses eligible for such credit; (2) exclude Pell and Supplemental Educational Opportunity Grants from types of scholarship assistance which reduce the allowable amount of such credit; and (3) exempt certain expenses eligible for such credit from tax information reporting requirements.\n\nMakes the Hope Scholarship and Lifetime Learning tax credits refundable."
  },
